  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1  \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Detention for Danis Ali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fort Magistrate Dilina Gamage has ordered that Danis Ali, who was accused of trespassing and threatening the Sri Lankan Rupavahini Corporation, be remanded until August 5th.",
        "He was arrested yesterday evening (26) from the flight which was ready for departure at Katunayake International Airport.",
        "This order was issued when he was produced before the judge and he was ordered to be produced before the Colombo Chief Magistrate's Court on August 1.",
        "He was arrested by the Criminal Investigation Department on a SriLankan Airlines flight which was about to take off for Dubai yesterday.",
        "At that time, the passengers were shocked and posted a video about it and expressed their displeasure.",
        "Danis Ali stated that he is not fleeing the country, he is traveling abroad to take the protest message to the international community and to present his case to the UN.",
        "When asked about having cut his hair and shaved his beard, Tanis said he did so at the request of his family and friends.",
        "The police said that he was arrested on July 13 for trespassing into the Sri Lanka Rupavahini Corporation, threatening the live broadcast and forcing the corporation to suspend its broadcast for a while and there are three charges against him.",
        "An arrest warrant has been issued for Danis Ali, who was detained and interrogated by the Criminal Investigation Department, when he was produced before the magistrate this evening."
      ],
